tool_description: Get the VCT contract information for all 3 regions via this API. Updated every few hours.
name: VCT Global Contract Database
title: VCT Global Contract Database

api_list.name: PACIFIC
api_list.description: Returns a json of all teams inside PACIFIC.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://vct-global-contract-database.p.rapidapi.com/PACIFIC.json"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "vct-global-contract-database.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
